      <dl>
        <dt><img src="http://caishuo.com/img/new/2.7_r4_c3.jpg" /></dt>
        <dd><img src="http://caishuo.com/img/new/2.7_r5_c6.png" /> <span>掏出微信扫一扫！</span><br />
        <span>或搜索微信公共账号：</span><br />
        <span>caishuo-caishuo</span></dd>
      </dl>

      <div class="micro-blog">新浪微博：<a href="http://weibo.com/touzhuti">@财说组合投资</a></div>
